{"tid":1811031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又中）中聯辦主任死因不單純？ 郭文貴：被幹掉的","createTime":"2020-01-04T10:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T21:26:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"018e4cc46890106b4818c6ebadd9586a75e0772c","tid":1811031,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:46:45.000Z","msg":"10月21日，中國國務院港澳事務辦公室發布消息稱，中國中央人民政府駐澳門特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任鄭曉松，因患抑鬱症於20日晚在其澳門住所墜樓身亡。然而其死因卻引發外界質疑。中國流亡富商郭文貴今日發布簡短影片爆料，鄭曉松「實際上是被幹掉的」，更說「香港的中聯辦，姓王的哥們也快了」。<br />\n<br />\n中國流亡富商郭文貴今日發布影片，表達對鄭曉松墜樓身亡的看法，「又自殺了！實際上是被幹掉的」，郭文貴爆料，「鄭曉松最好的哥們就是孟宏偉！」，似乎暗示鄭曉松之死與孟宏偉被失蹤事件有關聯。<br />\n<br />\n郭還表示，此二人和現任中國公安部副部長孫力軍是「拜把兄弟」，但也沒擋住孟宏偉被抓、鄭曉松被跳樓。郭還預告，「香港的中聯辦姓王的哥們也快了！大家往下看吧！」似乎是暗示現任香港中聯辦主任王志民將出事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2588210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2588210&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=1bbeb05a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2588210&h=dca8adaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2588210</a>"},{"pid":"98949d59a8c3b1a76f0c16dea9643e2a4b0238e8","tid":1811031,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"姓王嘅都隔咗兩個月先落台喎"},{"pid":"2f54b1c5abdaaf1db113ddc7f844b3abaf9f5736","tid":1811031,"uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"鳩upper中左次bor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e9804de26e9c578c3a9a7f36ea44c79b72052d","tid":1811031,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾期牆紙】 破局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=748b8b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aypmVes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaypmVes.jpg&h=462652b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34af288e2844f967b094214312ab8f4aedae292","tid":1811031,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"aa9f59490aa4f910245342c0342b1d7edae17ffd","tid":1811031,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f54b1c5abdaaf1db113ddc7f844b3abaf9f5736","tid":1811031,"uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"鳩upper中左次bor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"做共諜次次都錯就無人會信 , 間中都要中一兩單"},{"pid":"3d1d04685429c6d68b7621e410f6dabd38377fdf","tid":1811031,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">范</span></span>"},{"pid":"052bd27fe9be0abe033c9eefaa0dca840aac1049","tid":1811031,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92a294fb7735b09ab5cda6e5845bad6111654c7","tid":1811031,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說「新沙士」 <br />\n試著說「中國肺炎」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"42632a5cad63ade120bbffb634b7c2b41709298f","tid":1811031,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"我都識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a02a218e3cd4ba2b5deae594e82cb1e7d23edf","tid":1811031,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"喔"},{"pid":"9a9da4faf76c50237ace93fe05757c1953474a23","tid":1811031,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42632a5cad63ade120bbffb634b7c2b41709298f","tid":1811031,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"我都識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"早講吖馬"},{"pid":"92fa6dd4bf2e2ca453bb387a4da5ea1430d65acc","tid":1811031,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f54b1c5abdaaf1db113ddc7f844b3abaf9f5736","tid":1811031,"uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"鳩upper中左次bor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"中，不過一年之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>Oct 21, 2018</strong> - 周日（21日）早，中國國務院港澳事務辦公室發佈消息稱，中國中央人民政府駐澳門特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任鄭曉松於周六（10月20日）晚在其澳門住所墜樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n我都來預測下啦：林鄭三年之内一定下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ec1d0bcb36f2845d72babf95930bcebfb99df9","tid":1811031,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">清算黑警開始!</span>"},{"pid":"2be97fc07a92ce9aabed3067b45ef9451f795fcc","tid":1811031,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"鄭曉松，1959年9月生於北京，挪威奧斯陸大學挪威語專業畢業，曾喺1996年至1997年喺英國牛津大學外交官研究生班學習。<br />\n鄭曉松喺外交領域擔任公職。攞多外交部西歐司一等秘書，財政部國際司司長、部長助理，亞洲開發銀行中國執行董事，中共中央對外聯絡部副部長等職務。<br />\n習近平上台之後，鄭曉松獲得重用。2013年7月擔任福建副省長，其後仲擔任過中共福建省委常委、秘書長職。<br />\n中共十九大前一年，鄭曉松短暫調回中央，中央對外聯絡部副部長。<br />\n中共十九大前一個月，佢被任命為中國中央人民政府駐澳門特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任，喺副部晉升為正部。十九大上，佢入列中央委員。<br />\n<br />\n澳門中聯辦網站顯示，鄭曉松前一天即10月19號仲出席一場公開活動，喺寫字樓會見民聯智庫負責人。<br />\n官方稱，鄭曉松跳樓自殺係因罹患抑郁。中共十九大前夕，鄭曉松由中央對外聯絡部副部長一職調任澳門，去咗前履新一年零一個月。"},{"pid":"55e418f96765e248ad847ec2031726f6f565f420","tid":1811031,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98949d59a8c3b1a76f0c16dea9643e2a4b0238e8","tid":1811031,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"姓王嘅都隔咗兩個月先落台喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:26:03.000Z","msg":"係一年兩個月之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄭前年10月死"}]}